WEBVTT


00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:02.199
Muay Thai stance in under a minute.

00:00:02.200 --> 00:00:04.399
Heel toe about one and 1/2 times

00:00:04.400 --> 00:00:06.660
until your weights under your shoulders and hips.

00:00:06.680 --> 00:00:08.639
Pretend to wrap a towel around your head

00:00:08.640 --> 00:00:10.279
or be able to wipe your eyebrows.

00:00:10.280 --> 00:00:13.079
To have your hands up and don't flare your elbows,

00:00:13.080 --> 00:00:14.359
protect your ribs.

00:00:14.360 --> 00:00:16.319
To maintain a solid foundation,

00:00:16.320 --> 00:00:18.380
squeeze your glutes and your core.

00:00:18.440 --> 00:00:20.359
This allows you to be in an active stance.

00:00:20.360 --> 00:00:23.559
To check a kick or respond with your own at any time,

00:00:23.560 --> 00:00:25.140
keep your weight below you.

00:00:25.160 --> 00:00:26.119
Wanna move left,

00:00:26.120 --> 00:00:27.359
start with your left leg.

00:00:27.360 --> 00:00:28.519
Wanna move backwards,

00:00:28.520 --> 00:00:29.639
start with your back leg.

00:00:29.640 --> 00:00:31.119
To encourage good habits,

00:00:31.120 --> 00:00:34.119
practice an offensive or defensive move

